[:zh_CN] [`operation_not_permitted] [=--] [`pm] 为 [`nullptr]。

[item]
[:en] [`resource_deadlock_would_occur] [=--] if on entry [`owns] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`resource_deadlock_would_occur] [=--] 进入时 [`owns] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]
[exit:description]

